<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>IT-Labs</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,800;1,900&display=swap"
          rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@splidejs/splide@latest/dist/css/splide.min.css">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
<%- include("views/partials/header-before-login.ejs", {relativePath:""}) %>

<header class="header">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="grid__6">
                <h1 class="heading-primary heading-primary--main ro">Gaseste un programator pentru a primi ajutor
                    live</h1>
                <h1 class="heading-primary heading-primary--main en">Find a developer for
                    live mentorship</h1>
                <div class="nav__log-in">
                    <a href="/login" class="nav__log-in-btn ro">Gaseste pe cineva acum</a>
                    <a href="/login" class="nav__log-in-btn en">Get help now</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="grid__6">
                <img class="header__img" src="img/welcome.png" alt="">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<section class="u-vpadding color-section--primary">
    <div class="row">
        <h2 class="heading-secondary heading-secondary--grey-dark ro" style="color: #fff;">Cum functioneaza?</h2>
        <h2 class="heading-secondary heading-secondary--grey-dark en" style="color: #fff;">How it works?</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="timeline">
        <div class="timeline__item">
            <div class="timeline__container">
                <div class="timeline__text-box">
                    <h3 class="heading-tertiary ro">Pasul 1</h3>
                    <h3 class="heading-tertiary en">Step 1</h3>
                    <p class="paragraph ro">Pentru a beneficia de mentorat online pentru un anumit limbaj de programare,
                        mai intai trebuie
                        sa iti faci un cont de student, alegand butonul de "sign up" din meniul din partea superioara a
                        paginii.
                        In cazul in care ai mai multa experienta si vrei sa devii mentor, alege optiunea "become a
                        mentor" din acelasi meniu.

                    </p>
                    <p class="paragraph en">
                        In order to benefit from online mentoring for a certain programming language, you must first
                        create a student account, choosing the "sign up" button from the menu at the top of the page. If
                        you have more experience and want to become a mentor, choose the "become a mentor" option from
                        the same menu.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline__item">
            <div class="timeline__container">
                <div class="timeline__text-box">
                    <h3 class="heading-tertiary ro">Pasul 2</h3>
                    <h3 class="heading-tertiary en">Step 2</h3>
                    <p class="paragraph ro">Dupa ce studentul contacteaza mentorul dorit, ales in functie de interesele
                        lor
                        comune, cei doi stabilesc de comun acord o viitoare sesiune online.
                        Acum incepe adevarata experienta ITLabs!
                    </p>
                    <p class="paragraph en">
                        After the student contacts the desired mentor, chosen according to their interests
                        jointly, the two agree on a future online session.
                        Now the real ITLabs experience begins!
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline__item">
            <div class="timeline__container">
                <div class="timeline__text-box">
                    <h3 class="heading-tertiary ro">Pasul 3</h3>
                    <h3 class="heading-tertiary en">Step 3</h3>
                    <p class="paragraph ro">
                        In cadrul sesiunilor de mentorat online aveti ocazia de a comunica atat in scris, cat si audio
                        si video. Mai mult decat atat,
                        veti avea la dispozitie un spatiu comun pentru scrierea de cod, dar si o tabla comuna unde
                        puteti desena.
                        Speram sa te simti in largul tau alaturi de noi. Spor la munca!
                    </p>
                    <p class="paragraph en">
                        During the online mentoring sessions you have the opportunity to communicate both in writing and
                        audio
                        and video. More than that,
                        you will have at your disposal a common space for writing code, but also a common board where
                        you can draw.
                        We hope you feel at ease with us. Good luck with your work!
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    </div>
</section>

